### 3.1 Kontrakt na System Pro dla Jana (ClientId=1, SoftwareId=1)
# Cena: BasePrice=5000, zniżka letnia 10% → 4500, +1 rok wsparcia (2 lata) → +1000 = 5500
# EndDate musi być 3-30 dni od dziś
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/contracts/create-Contract
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "clientId": 1,
  "softwareId": 1,
  "endDate": "2026-07-10T00:00:00",
  "yearsOfSupport": 2
}

### 3.2 Kontrakt na FinanceTracker dla firmy TechCorp (ClientId=3, SoftwareId=3)
